text: Manitowoc () is a city in and the county seat of Manitowoc County, Wisconsin, United States. The city is located on Lake Michigan at the mouth of the Manitowoc River. According to the 2020 census, Manitowoc had a population of 34,626. ==Sister city== Manitowoc has one sister city: * Kamogawa, Japan ==References== ==External links== * City of Manitowoc * Manitowoc Area Visitor & Convention Bureau * Manitowoc Local History Collection at the University of Wisconsin Digital Collections Category:County seats in Wisconsin Category:Cities in Wisconsin
